# Using clang-format v18.0.0
# https://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormatStyleOptions.html
# Reference link: https://github.com/sevanetrebchenko/clang-format-c
# { BasedOnStyle: Google, AlignArrayOfStructures: Left, AlignConsecutiveAssignments: AcrossComments, AlignConsecutiveBitFields: AcrossComments, AlignConsecutiveMacros: AcrossEmptyLinesAndComments, AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: None, ColumnLimit: 0, IndentWidth: 4, ReflowComments: true }

---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: Google
AlignArrayOfStructures: Left
AlignConsecutiveAssignments: AcrossComments
AlignConsecutiveBitFields: AcrossComments
AlignConsecutiveMacros: AcrossEmptyLinesAndComments
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: None
ColumnLimit: 0
IndentWidth: 4
ReflowComments: true
---
